// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2021-0427 — Mass File Rename (blackbyte)
// Status: deprecated | Level: high | ID: 7048bcac-c502-5185-8639-ce83661092c2

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
